Donnie Dunagan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Donnie_Dunagan 0 Donald "Donnie" Roan Dunagan (born August 16, 1934) is an American former child actor and United States Marine Corps drill instructor. He was a voice actor in the Bambi film, providing the voice of young Bambi.
